    <h4>Shortcuts</h4>
    <p>Little addon was added to quickly open modal windows for adding things to report. Shortcuts are:</p>
    <dl class="dl-horizontal">
        <dt>R or r</dt>
        <dd>Open a modular window with Add Re-Issue</dd>
        <dt>P or p</dt>
        <dd>Open a modular window with Add Printer</dd>
        <dt>C or c</dt>
        <dd>Open a modular window with Add Pre-Check</dd>
        <dt>W or w</dt>
        <dd>Open a modular window with Add Password</dd>
        <dt>H or h</dt>
        <dd>Open a modular window with Add Hour Overtime</dd>
        <dt>M or m</dt>
        <dd>Open a modular window with Add Main Task</dd>
    </dl>
    <p>Shortcuts only work if the page is in foreground and is in focus. Wont work when focus is on another window or is active write cursor at any inputs for data.</p>

