    <h4>Requirement for filling forms</h4>
    <p>Each forms for adding - Re-Issue,Printers,PreCheck,Password,Hour Overtime,Main Task are required to fill except few inputs:</p>
    <dl class="dl-horizontal">
        <dt>Re-Issue</dt>
        <dd><strong><span class="text-danger text-uppercase">Each inputs must be filled!</span></strong></dd>
        <dt>Printers</dt>
        <dd><strong><span class="text-danger text-uppercase">Each inputs must be filled!</span></strong></dd>
        <dt>PreCheck</dt>
        <dd><strong><span class="text-danger text-uppercase">Time, System, Check - must be filled.</span></strong> Email Time can be empty.</dd>
        <dt>Password</dt>
        <dd><strong><span class="text-danger text-uppercase">Each inputs must be filled!</span></strong></dd>
        <dt>Hour OverTime</dt>
        <dd><strong><span class="text-danger text-uppercase">Time, Duration, Shop, Type, Description - must be filled!</span></strong> Cooperation can be empty.</dd>
        <dt>Main Task</dt>
        <dd><strong><span class="text-danger text-uppercase">Time, Duration, Shop, System, What happened, How it was solved - must be filled!</span></strong> Cooperation can be empty.</dd>
    </dl>
